title: Ely Stays Undefeated, Wins Section 7 Title
text:
Ely Stays Undefeated, Wins Section 7 Title 
By Zach Schneider October 23, 2015 Updated Oct 23, 2015 at 10:49 PM CDT 
Esko, MN (NNCNOW.com) --- The Ely football team put together a dominant defensive performance on Friday night, beating Cook County 27-0 in the Section 7 9-Man championship game at Les Knuti Field. 
This will mark the Timberwolves' third trip to the state tournament in the past four seasons, having also gone in 2012 and 2013.
